==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Disponge
<hw>Dis*ponge"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>dis-</ets> + <ets>sponge</ets>.]</ety> <def>To sprinkle, as with
water from a sponge.</def> <mark>[Poetic & Rare]</mark> <altsp>[Written
also <asp>dispunge</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>O sovereign mistress of true melancholy,⟦br⟧
The poisonous damp of night <qex>disponge</qex> upon me</q>.
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dispope</ent>⟦br⟧
